title: SEP Sesam Backup Job
agents: sep_sesam
catalog: app/backup
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Monitors the status of individual SEP Sesam backup tasks.

 Each backup task within a backup group is discovered as a separate
 service. The check reports OK if the last run was SUCCESSFUL,
 WARNING for WARNING status, and CRITICAL for ERROR or CANCELLED.

item:
 The name of the backup task.
